e out the same day to diagnose and fix the problem. The technician was knowledgeable, friendly, and explained everything clearly. They had the issue repaired quickly, and my hot water was back in no time. The pricing was fair, and the service was top-notch. I’m so grateful for their expertise and professionalism. I highly recommend them for any of your HVAC needs","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Chelsea cooling and heating was fantastic! My water heater stopped working, and they came out the same day to diagnose and fix the problem. The technician was knowledgeable, friendly, and explained everything clearly. They had the issue repaired quickly, and my hot water was back in no time. The pricing was fair, and the service was top-notch. I’m so grateful for their expertise and professionalism. I highly recommend them for any of your HVAC needs","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Jordan A. Babayoff","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102927662677028448009/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6vfoMyiyFFrfuAyGJWO57yx7ToqLfqTOl26IzmDs2QS0eaW1W=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"},"publishTime":"2025-01-28T23:04:49.049984Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURfNFlMVzJnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURfNFlMVzJnRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c259bcc50743eb:0xb4d67e91a933285a"},{"name":"places/ChIJ60MHxbxZwokRWigzqZF-1rQ/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VLU2wwNGFtOGJEQ2NREAE","relativePublishTimeDescription":"9 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I hired them last month to replace my HVAC unit before summertime. I was referred to them and really glad I was. They did a great job installing the new unit and the price was very reasonable. Very trustworthy and professional company.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I hired them last month to replace my HVAC unit before summertime. I was referred to them and really glad I was. They did a great job installing the new unit and the price was very reasonable. Very trustworthy and professional company.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Merav Alalo","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117891481119479844359/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdlPgXGHqsyODJGnMFhAHg3arY9tZuD7dI6H8EumJLBjLq4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-05-06T20:03:33.492493Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VLU2wwNGFtOGJEQ2NREAE&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VLU2wwNGFtOGJEQ2NREAE!2m1!1s0x89c259bcc50743eb:0xb4d67e91a933285a"},{"name":"places/ChIJ60MHxbxZwokRWigzqZF-1rQ/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNBbE5ydzR3RRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a year ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Great service and great people at Chelsea Cooling and Heating. We scheduled a routine maintenance check for our heating system. They thoroughly cleaned the area and equipment to assess for any potential issues, and ensured everything was running at peak efficiency. One part was replaced that could have caused a breakdown in the middle of winter, happy they caught that. Friendly, professional, and honest company!! Our system is running great. Thanks guys!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Great service and great people at Chelsea Cooling and Heating. We scheduled a routine maintenance check for our heating system. They thoroughly cleaned the area and equipment to assess for any potential issues, and ensured everything was running at peak efficiency. One part was replaced that could have caused a breakdown in the middle of winter, happy they caught that. Friendly, professional, and honest company!! Our system is running great. Thanks guys!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Kenneth Ian Panganiban","uri":"https://ww